headline: Assessing Lam Research (LRCX) Valuation After a 132% Year-to-Date Surge
summary: Lam Research (LRCX) has been on a quiet tear this year, with the stock up roughly 132% year to date and about 46% over the past 3 months, easily outpacing many chip peers. See our latest analysis for Lam Research. That surge in the 90 day share price return, alongside a triple digit year to date share price gain, suggests momentum is still building as investors lean into Lam's foundry and AI related demand story.
